name: 07/12/2021 TRASH($TRSH) DAY
description:
The past 1 1/2 years, hundreds(to thousands now I believe) of cryptoartists from all over the world have made at least one piece in the #Trashart aesthetic or in tribute to the original piece that started the meme, the '64 GALLON TOTER.'  This piece is a commemorative Trash .Gif(which is really an .Mp4 but that's just what we call the aesthetic) made for cryptoart world community at large.  It's been a wild ride changing the art world thus far, and we've only just begun.  Cheers to the Electric Renaissance.....XOXO

Also, if you wish to view a small fraction of works that have been created around the world, feel free to check out Trsh.Capital (web address) and it'll beam you into a cryptovoxels gallery showcasing these said pieces.
